        <description>&lt;img src="https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/featured-image.png" alt="Featured image of post VMUG Connect 2026 | Minneapolis" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VMUG Connect 2026:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://connect.vmug.com/minneapolis/2026/content&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;VMUG Connect 2026 in Minneapolis&lt;/a&gt; is the first that I will be presenting outside of my local VMUG or VMware Explore. I am looking forward to the event to share my vCommunity story.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/vmug-connect-2026-01.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1472&#34;
