	srcset=&#34;https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/vmug-connect-2026-01_hu_a2b915d45367c983.png 480w, https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/vmug-connect-2026-01_hu_e54edab0156feda1.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;209&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;501px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-path-to-influence-from-vmug-attendee-to-vexpert-blogger-and-conference-speaker&#34;&gt;The Path to Influence: From VMUG Attendee to vExpert, Blogger, and Conference Speaker
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Session Details:&lt;/strong&gt;
If you&amp;rsquo;ve ever felt the urge to present at a VMUG or start a technical blog but hesitated, this session is for you. At my first VMUG event, I was asking myself, &amp;ldquo;Can I do this?&amp;rdquo; My story is about setting a goal and finding fulfillment in the vCommunity by operating under one simple metric: If even a single person learns something new, the effort was worthwhile. Hear the personal story behind my decision to give back, the steps I took, and how you can start your own journey of presenting and contributing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My presentation schedule for VMUG Connect Minneapolis is finalized. I am involved in the following presentations and co-presentations during the conference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Consider attending &amp;ldquo;VMware Hands-On Lab: Monitoring Your Private Cloud Platform with VCF Operations (HOL-2610-03)&amp;rdquo; if you have not participated in an Expert-Led Workshop (ELW). While we use the HOL as a foundation, the session is driven by attendee questions and interests. We will explore features and configurations not covered in the standard lab guide. 👍🏻&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/vmug-connect-2026-02.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1197&#34;
	height=&#34;415&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/vmug-connect-2026-02_hu_6438920433f86d3e.png 480w, https://vcrocs.info/vmug-connect-2026-minneapolis/vmug-connect-2026-02_hu_6dd6905d8b95c8fb.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;288&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;692px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ll be using this blog as my official VMUG Connect Diary, so check back often.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I hope my story gives you a glimpse into what makes the vCommunity so special. I look forward to contributing to the vCommunity for years to come. I encourage you to start your own journey today; the community is ready to welcome you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I look forward to my first trip to Minneapolis and the opportunity to engage with the vCommunity members in the region.  Maybe I will even have a &amp;ldquo;Jucy Lucy&amp;rdquo; while in town.&lt;/p&gt;
